## getDeployedAssetAddress

## overridedTokens
```solidity
  mapping(bytes32 => struct DeBridgeTokenDeployer.OverridedTokenInfo) public overridedTokens;
```
Maps debridge id to overridden token info (name, symbol). Used when autogenerated
values for a token are not ideal.
